 I will only know to me personally. 

00:00:43.670 --> 00:00:46.853
 Comment on things that are important to me and George Walker Bush 

00:00:48.069 --> 00:00:50.503
 Well, as some of you remember 

00:00:50.503 --> 00:00:53.111
 The controversy over the 2000 presidential election lasted for several weeks 

00:00:53.604 --> 00:00:57.570
 Finally, Bush became president. 

00:00:57.570 --> 00:01:00.620
 At the time they planned to hold an inauguration ceremony in Washington. 

00:01:01.374 --> 00:01:04.874
 I remember that my wife and I were the only two volunteers to participate. 

00:01:04.874 --> 00:01:06.469
 Democrat 

00:01:07.669 --> 00:01:10.403
 Then George and Laura came over. 

00:01:10.403 --> 00:01:12.028
 Thanks for my arrival 

00:01:12.936 --> 00:01:16.639
 Then he said: "If I can help you with anything, please let me know." 

00:01:17.209 --> 00:01:19.070
 He made a mistake 

00:01:19.070 --> 00:01:20.375
 (laughter) 

00:01:20.375 --> 00:01:22.541
 I said, "Mr. President, Carter has projects in 35 countries around the world. 

00:01:22.541 --> 00:01:25.736
 The most serious problem now is 

00:01:25.736 --> 00:01:29.729
 War between North Sudan and South Sudan 

00:01:30.791 --> 00:01:33.137
 Thousands of people are being killed. 

00:01:33.137 --> 00:01:36.537
 I want to ask you to help us to reach a peace agreement there. 

00:01:37.168 --> 00:01:39.408
 At his most vulnerable time he said: "I will do it." 

00:01:39.670 --> 00:01:44.136
 Then I said, "When can I see your Secretary of State and the National Security Adviser?" 

00:01:44.136 --> 00:01:48.285
 He said: "I haven't chosen yet. Give us three weeks." 

00:01:48.624 --> 00:01:52.403
 Three weeks later I saw Colin Powell and Condoleezza Rice. 

00:01:52.403 --> 00:01:55.012
 President Bush fulfilled his promise 

00:01:55.336 --> 00:01:59.708
 He appointed John Dantfoss of Missouri, an outstanding senator 

00:01:59.708 --> 00:02:03.503
