00:02:11.236 --> 00:02:14.236
 Ended the 21-year war 

00:02:14.236 --> 00:02:16.236
 George Walker Bush is the promoter of this matter 

00:02:16.236 --> 00:02:22.503
 (applaud) 

00:02:22.503 --> 00:02:26.737
 This is his first great contribution to African countries. 

00:02:26.737 --> 00:02:29.268
 As I mentioned briefly 

00:02:29.268 --> 00:02:32.904
 He increased his development assistance to Africa 

00:02:32.904 --> 00:02:35.170
 Within his tenure 

00:02:35.170 --> 00:02:39.536
 (to increase the amount of aid) from $1.4 billion to $9 billion 

00:02:39.536 --> 00:02:43.051
 The growth rate reached 640% 

00:02:43.436 --> 00:02:45.277
 This is part of development assistance 

00:02:45.277 --> 00:02:47.668
 (applaud) 

00:02:47.668 --> 00:02:49.098
 He founded PEPFAR (Presidential Assistance AIDS Program) 

00:02:49.437 --> 00:02:52.669
 When he took office, only 50,000 AIDS patients in Africa were rescued. 

00:02:52.669 --> 00:02:53.958
 When he left, 

00:02:54.143 --> 00:02:56.570
 (The patient who received the help is 2 million) 

00:02:56.570 --> 00:02:58.620
 Let's count the percentage of growth. 

00:02:58.620 --> 00:02:59.752
 (applaud) 

00:02:59.752 --> 00:03:01.269
 Now with this new institution 

00:03:01.269 --> 00:03:04.011
 He has a project to teach "fans", "red ribbons" 

00:03:05.104 --> 00:03:07.810
 To help sub-Saharan Africa 

00:03:07.810 --> 00:03:09.669
 Women with cervical and breast cancer 

00:03:09.669 --> 00:03:11.809
 This is another act that makes me feel 

00:03:11.809 --> 00:03:15.571
 I know what it means for millions of African people. 

